{"tid":2008278,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多區悼梓樂 「港人未放棄過你」","createTime":"2020-05-09T02:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T13:15:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18acb4c15086f25e6b6395b49aafd4149d4eb09c","tid":2008278,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200509/BPIYY7KQVGQULX2BPT7ZQKRXQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200509%2FBPIYY7KQVGQULX2BPT7ZQKRXQA%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d4bsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=195d5fc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200509%2FBPIYY7KQVGQULX2BPT7ZQKRXQA%2F&h=5a9d0045\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200509/BPIYY7KQVGQULX2BPT7ZQKRXQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n多區悼梓樂 「港人未放棄過你」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日科大學生周梓樂逝世六個月，屯門、元朗、天水圍及科大校園等區均有悼念活動。警方在屯門大會堂駐重兵，派半百警設起封鎖線，截查及驅趕途經的市民；元朗有市民到西鐵站連儂牆摺紙鶴及獻花，強調港人不因疫情而丟淡事件，「想同周同學講香港人並未放棄過你」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：60警衝入ifc噴椒 屈市民犯聚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200509/large/1588955477_f230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200509%2Flarge%2F1588955477_f230.jpg&h=6cd7163a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角有市民舉行悼念活動，警拉起封鎖線截查途人。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n科大生校園獻花<br />\n<br />\n有網民發起昨晚8時各區悼念周梓樂，當中屯門大會堂傍晚6時起，已有約半百防暴、軍裝及便衣警戒備，約8時湧上屯門大會堂拉起封鎖線，截查途經市民，及後有民眾走出屯門市廣場外唱《願榮光歸香港》，又高叫五大訴求等口號。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n元朗西鐵站對開連儂牆，晚上陸續有市民到場致祭，不少人獻花及默哀。陳小姐稱心情較沉重，因個人能力有限，望透過摺紙鶴表達和平與希望，亦相信港人毋忘事件，樂見抗爭遍地開花。<br />\n<br />\n科大校園傍晚6時在賽馬會大堂有追悼會，校方早前向師生發電郵表明不允許公眾集會，警告參與即屬違法，或遭校內紀律處分，但學生代表堅持如期舉行，同學。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另有網民發起在旺角、黃大仙及尖沙嘴「三區開花」，其中在旺角，晚上近9時數十名防暴警突湧向西洋菜南街近百老匯戲院對開。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者馮智敏、司徒韋桐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200509/large/1588955477_a4eb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200509%2Flarge%2F1588955477_a4eb.gif&h=376b3ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n科大校園內設周梓樂追悼會，學生排隊逐一鞠躬及獻花。科大電台新聞組fb圖片"},{"pid":"4267959b818107cf8ec15bdf632e85b5e0b72af8","tid":2008278,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"但尚德已經封鬼哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出事位置入唔到"},{"pid":"89273ddd25bd1e4f709ec41f52396a617d5086f3","tid":2008278,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4267959b818107cf8ec15bdf632e85b5e0b72af8","tid":2008278,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"但尚德已經封鬼哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出事位置入唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:47:21.000Z","msg":"真。害怕正義<br />\n曱甴身有屎仲有血"},{"pid":"2df258fa4f867aae74060960f3a5e32e111f1ad4","tid":2008278,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16b333c405f3a627b544affafefce154dfc8cd3","tid":2008278,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bbc6db422b12c61108a397b712936b55389eb9e","tid":2008278,"uid":299991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T02:56:43.000Z","msg":"咪送頭， 昨晚又係咁"},{"pid":"18ed47f33ac4cd2873cf91d928f67379b7204ecd","tid":2008278,"uid":306689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"用二丶三十人一隊，分散一萬個隨機地方，不要集中。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}